short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Convert JPG files to EPS format

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
How to convert JPG to EPS?	 

1-Click extension icon - this will open JPG to EPS online conversion website. 
2-Select JPG file and click convert button. 
3-You will get your EPS file download link in your email address.
